{"tid":1985963,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個控制唔到自己嘅時刻","createTime":"2020-04-23T13:42:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-23T13:54:08.000Z","uid":205742,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f823cc12e28e2d004850d11f5e2b0c52b68de004","tid":1985963,"uid":205742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T13:42:35.000Z","msg":"細個去鬼屋玩太high ，控制唔到自己係咁大叫 <br />\n<br />\n有啲裝道具丶恐怖野嘅枱 我好大力咁推張檯，<br />\n撞去鬼屋啲圍板<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呯！...呯！....呯 ！！！<br />\n姐係好似拍戲俾人困住咗咁，之後拎架車仔不斷撞道牆咁 撞左成分鐘覺得攰先至繼續行 嗰時又冇人阻我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我仲好記得同行嘅大人都笑到仆街 好彩嗰時未有Facebook 如果唔係我應該俾人笑成世<br />\n<br />\n依家如果唔係同女仔去 真係唔會浪費自己時間 心血少<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cf7d7d593ed35d91db3e53d26c13d5db42a212d","tid":1985963,"uid":205742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T13:43:24.000Z","msg":"嗰時算唔算鬼上身 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但我又記得好清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be00d811e27813cab3ea83fbd3de67b4c51312ba","tid":1985963,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T13:43:38.000Z","msg":"富士山"},{"pid":"18d263be8831ea6670fcfa6be02d7b820e6a789d","tid":1985963,"uid":205742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be00d811e27813cab3ea83fbd3de67b4c51312ba","tid":1985963,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T13:43:38.000Z","msg":"富士山"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T13:44:41.000Z","msg":"唔明"},{"pid":"e71cf0f81caf34e74c45aa9efc237c2bffcba826","tid":1985963,"uid":205742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit